## 2. Routing — Where do I write?

| Intent | File |
|---|---|
| Architectural decision (append-only) | `.agent_works/decisions.md` |
| Multi-step plan | `.agent_works/plans.md` |
| Requirements / scope / north star | `.agent_works/project_requirements.md` |
| Handoff to next session (replace each session) | `.agent_works/handoff/current_handoff.md` |
| Work tickets | `.agent_works/coordination/work_queue.md` |
| Ephemeral scratch | `.local/<topic>/` |
| User-facing onboarding | `README.md` |
| Permission tweaks (Claude Code) | `.claude/settings.local.json` |

**Source-of-truth priority** (top wins on conflict):
`AGENTS.md` → `project_requirements.md` → `decisions.md` → `plans.md` →
`current_handoff.md` → `README.md`.

_If `plans.md` / `project_requirements.md` are absent (minimal
layout), create them from this routing table on first need._

